videos.description: Quinton Flowers throws a screen pass to Tyre McCants who breaks tackles to go 47 yards and dives in with a defender dragging behind for the Bulls.
videos.headline: McCants drags defender to end zone for USF TD

videos.description: UCF QB McKenzie Milton fools the defense with a spin to get outside and ties the game with a three-yard touchdown run for the Knights.
videos.headline: Milton spins for UCF TD

videos.description: McKenzie Milton buys time and throws back across the field to the back of the end zone where Dredrick Snelson leaps to make a great grab for the Knights.
videos.headline: UCF's Snelson reaches for great TD catch

videos.description: Tyre McCants gets in the right spot between two defenders on a 55-yard pass from Quinton Flowers for the Bulls.
videos.headline: McCants gets another huge gain for South Florida

videos.description: McKenzie Milton fakes the pitch and then actually pitches to Adrian Killins Jr. for a 5-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Milton pitches to Killins Jr. for UCF TD

videos.description: Tyre McCants finds space on the sideline for another 55-yard catch from Quinton Flowers for South Florida.
videos.headline: McCants gets open for big gain

videos.description: Quinton Flowers fires a 20-yard touchdown pass to Temi Alaka who leaps up over his defender to bring down the ball for the Bulls.
videos.headline: Alaka gets way up for South Florida TD catch

videos.description: Quinton Flowers spins out of the grasp of a rusher and finds Tyre McCants down the sideline for 33 yards on third down.
videos.headline: Flowers escapes sack to find McCants for Bulls

videos.description: Quinton Flowers finds Mitchell Wilcox over the top for a 21-yard touchdown cutting UCF's lead to 21-20.
videos.headline: Wilcox battles with defender for South Florida TD

videos.description: South Florida QB Quinton Flowers is picked off by a diving Mike Hughes to end the first half.
videos.headline: Hughes makes diving interception for Knights

videos.description: UCF head coach Scott Frost says his team needs to make adjustments after their drop off in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Frost: 'We've gotta find our rhythm again'

videos.description: UCF QB McKenzie Milton connects with Gabriel Davis on a 23-yard touchdown pass for his second passing and fourth total touchdown today.
videos.headline: Milton finds Davis for 4th TD

videos.description: Darius Tice takes the direct snap and picks up a block on this six-yard touchdown run for the Bulls.
videos.headline: Tice pushes through for short South Florida TD

videos.description: Quinton Flowers finds a hole and makes his way to the end zone on a 24-yard touchdown run for the Bulls.
videos.headline: Flowers scrambles for TD to give South Florida the lead

videos.description: McKenzie Milton launches a 45-yard touchdown pass to a wide open Dredrick Snelson to put UCF ahead 35-34.
videos.headline: Snelson gets wide open for huge UCF TD

videos.description: Darnell Solomon leaps to keep South Florida's drive alive on a desperation heave from Quinton Flowers for a 20-yard gain.
videos.headline: South Florida's Solomon makes incredible catch on third-and-18

videos.description: Otis Anderson gets the short pass and finds a lane to score a 23-yard touchdown putting UCF up 42-34.
videos.headline: Anderson scores on screen pass for UCF TD
